@startuml FaunaConnect2 - Deployment Diagram
title FaunaConnect2 Deployment Diagram

package "FaunaConnect2" {

  package "Frontend" {
    component "MAUI App\n(Android)" as ANDROID
    component "MAUI App\n(Windows)" as WINDOWS
  }

  package "Backend" {
    component "Web API\n(ASP.NET Core)" as API
    component "SQLite Database" as DB
  }

}

ANDROID --> API : Consumes
WINDOWS --> API : Consumes
API --> DB : Connects to

@enduml